    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为教育LMS门户设计一个程序执行的状态流转图。核心场景是：学员从门户加载学习程序，经过验证后运行，过程中可能暂停，也可能需要进入着装准备环节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Validating",
        "Running",
        "Paused",
        "Dressing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我梳理一下：门户初始状态是Idle，加载后进入Loading，然后验证。如果验证失败要处理错误对吧？验证通过才到Ready状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Validating",
        "Ready",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，验证失败进入Error状态，需要手动清除错误才能回到Idle。验证通过到Ready后，学员可以启动程序进入Running。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Validating",
        "Error",
        "Ready",
        "Running",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Running状态我考虑几种分支：学员可以暂停，或者程序正常结束到Complete。您提到的着装准备是什么触发条件？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Paused",
        "Complete",
        "Dressing"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "有些实训课程需要特定着装，Running时如果检测到需要着装，就进入Dressing状态，完成后返回Running。另外暂停和恢复要有明确的命令触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Dressing",
        "Paused",
        "Resume Command",
        "Pause Command"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我构建一下：Running通过Pause Command到Paused，Paused通过Resume Command回到Running；Running通过Dress Required到Dressing，Dressing通过Dress Complete返回Running。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Paused",
        "Dressing",
        "Pause Command",
        "Resume Command",
        "Dress Required",
        "Dress Complete"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "程序结束到Complete之后呢？应该能重置回Idle重新开始。还有Loading到Validating的触发条件，用Program Loaded合适吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Complete",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Validating",
        "Program Loaded"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认：Complete通过Reset回到Idle，Loading通过Program Loaded进入Validating，Error通过Clear Error回到Idle。这样整个闭环就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Complete",
        "Idle",
        "Loading",
        "Validating",
        "Error",
        "Reset",
        "Program Loaded",
        "Clear Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "最后检查Running到Complete的触发条件，用Program End表示程序正常结束。Ready到Running用Start Program。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Complete",
        "Ready",
